<TEXT>
   Stocks went nowhere today in what Wall Street
brokers described as listless dog-day trading.
   ``There's really nothing going on. The floor is very quiet,''
said Charles Eaton, a market strategist at Nikko Securities Co.
International in New York.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrial stocks, which rose 24
