vacationing. Others said professional investors were awaiting a
more telling report on the economy's direction, the August
unemployment data released Friday by the Labor Department.
   Among the blue chip stocks, McDonalds was off \ to 43], IBM was
off ] to 113 and Procter & Gamble was up \ to 74~.
